title: Ozzy and Jack's World Tour Season 1 [Complete]
description:
Ozzy & Jack's World Detour is an American reality television series starring Ozzy Osbourne and his son Jack Osbourne. The series premiered on July 24, 2016, on History. During each episode, Ozzy and Jack visit one or more sites to learn about their history from experts and explore unusual or quirky aspects of their background.

Episodes

1 - Like Forefathers, Like Sons
2 - Remember the Alamo?
3 - Father Knows West
4 - Unidentified Flying Ozzy
5 - Iron Mountain Men
6 - Sir Prince of Darkness
7 - The Last Two Samurai
8 - Misters Osbourne Go to Washington
9 - Cuba or Busted
10 - The Devil Made Me Do It
